We have not yet been able to verify

00:00:05.338 --> 00:00:06.506
if people were actually killed

00:00:06.506 --> 00:00:07.007
in this moment.

00:00:07.007 --> 00:00:08.775
If you're actually looking at people die

00:00:08.775 --> 00:00:09.909
behind those doors.

00:00:09.909 --> 00:00:11.411
But obviously, that was the plan.

00:00:11.411 --> 00:00:12.245
That was the intent.

00:00:12.245 --> 00:00:13.446
That's what they were doing.

00:00:13.446 --> 00:00:14.647
And CNN is analyzing

00:00:14.647 --> 00:00:17.317
and verifying more than 50 videos

00:00:17.317 --> 00:00:20.053
like this one, piecing together exactly

