00:00:24.691 --> 00:00:26.159
Katie Polglase is OUTFRONT

00:00:26.159 --> 00:00:33.533
with an in-depth investigation.

00:00:33.633 --> 00:00:35.168
It's 6:30 a.m.

00:00:35.168 --> 00:00:36.269
on October 7th,

00:00:36.269 --> 00:00:37.570
and things are getting into full

00:00:37.570 --> 00:00:39.339
swing at the Nova Festival

00:00:39.339 --> 00:00:42.175
in the south of Israel.

00:00:42.175 --> 00:00:43.710
We were having fun.

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:45.045
You know, peace, love,

00:00:45.045 --> 00:00:46.913
good vibes and an hour

00:00:46.913 --> 00:00:47.647
or an hour and a half

00:00:47.647 --> 00:00:50.216
after we are running from bullets,

00:00:50.216 --> 00:00:54.421
suddenly the music stops.

00:00:54.521 --> 00:00:56.289
And then

00:00:56.289 --> 00:00:57.357
there's the station.

00:00:57.357 --> 00:00:59.125
But no sense yet of the horror

00:00:59.125 --> 00:01:00.760
about to unfold

00:01:00.760 --> 00:01:01.194
as news

00:01:01.194 --> 00:01:02.062
spreads of rocket

00:01:02.062 --> 00:01:03.696
attacks from Gaza, people

00:01:03.696 --> 00:01:05.198
begin seeking shelter,

00:01:05.198 --> 00:01:07.567
crouching close to the ground.

00:01:07.567 --> 00:01:08.535
But even this doesn't

00:01:08.535 --> 00:01:10.170
lead to outright panic.

00:01:10.170 --> 00:01:10.937
Rocket attacks

00:01:10.937 --> 00:01:11.404
visible

00:01:11.404 --> 00:01:13.073
here are a regular occurrence

00:01:13.073 --> 00:01:15.475
in this part of southern Israel.

00:01:15.475 --> 00:01:16.843
About 10 minutes later

00:01:16.843 --> 00:01:19.412
and some start heading to their cars.

00:01:19.412 --> 00:01:20.580
The decision of when

00:01:20.580 --> 00:01:22.449
and how to leave the festival

00:01:22.449 --> 00:01:28.221
would mean life or death for many.

00:01:28.321 --> 00:01:30.990
Some fled early to nearby bomb shelters.

00:01:30.990 --> 00:01:32.292
It's 7:10 a.m.

00:01:32.292 --> 00:01:33.860
and many are crammed inside.

00:01:33.860 --> 00:01:36.196
This one to the north of the festival.

00:01:36.196 --> 00:01:38.498
But they've been followed.

00:01:38.498 --> 00:01:40.867
At 7:24 a.m., Hamas

00:01:40.867 --> 00:01:42.435
threw a grenade inside,

00:01:42.435 --> 00:01:45.171
causing horrific damage.

00:01:45.171 --> 00:01:46.139
This man, Noah,

00:01:46.139 --> 00:01:49.042
emerges stunned into the daylight

00:01:49.042 --> 00:01:50.376
and is not the only shelter

00:01:50.376 --> 00:01:51.344
to be targeted.

00:01:51.344 --> 00:01:52.479
30 minutes later

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:54.314
and further down the same road,

00:01:54.314 --> 00:01:55.582
Hamas militants are caught

00:01:55.582 --> 00:01:56.950
on dashcam footage

00:01:56.950 --> 00:01:58.985
outside another shelter.

00:01:58.985 --> 00:02:01.521
They throw a grenade inside.

00:02:01.521 --> 00:02:03.389
In total, CNN has identified

00:02:03.389 --> 00:02:04.657
four different shelters

00:02:04.657 --> 00:02:05.658
near the festival.

00:02:05.658 --> 00:02:06.993
The Hamas attacks

00:02:06.993 --> 00:02:10.163
all full of people over the next 6 hours.

00:02:10.196 --> 00:02:12.165
Hundreds of civilians were killed,

00:02:12.165 --> 00:02:13.566
hunted down as they tried

00:02:13.566 --> 00:02:15.135
to flee the festival

00:02:15.135 --> 00:02:16.236
by examining over

00:02:16.236 --> 00:02:18.037
50 videos of that morning

00:02:18.037 --> 00:02:19.939
and speaking to 12 survivors.

00:02:19.939 --> 00:02:21.841
CNN has established that Hamas

00:02:21.841 --> 00:02:23.409
surrounded the festival,

00:02:23.409 --> 00:02:24.878
blocking three approaches

00:02:24.878 --> 00:02:26.279
to the south, north

00:02:26.279 --> 00:02:27.247
and west,

00:02:27.247 --> 00:02:29.048
forcing people to flee across

00:02:29.048 --> 00:02:31.384
the fields to the east.

00:02:31.451 --> 00:02:33.620
Even then, they were hunted.

00:02:33.620 --> 00:02:36.022
It's now 8:15 a.m., and Gal Brooke

00:02:36.022 --> 00:02:38.124
Chopin survives along with others

00:02:38.124 --> 00:02:39.859
by running across the fields.

00:02:39.859 --> 00:02:42.295
He's pictured here in the white T-shirt.

00:02:42.295 --> 00:02:43.796
Local police and security

00:02:43.796 --> 00:02:44.764
told them to drive

00:02:44.764 --> 00:02:46.466
east across rough land

00:02:46.466 --> 00:02:48.501
due to roadblocks on the main road.

00:02:48.501 --> 00:02:50.737
But many end up fleeing on foot.

00:02:50.737 --> 00:02:51.604
We're like ducks.

00:02:51.604 --> 00:02:52.672
It was like a range.

00:02:52.672 --> 00:02:55.675
People were running in their hundreds.

00:02:55.875 --> 00:02:57.744
And you can hear the bullets coming.

00:02:57.744 --> 00:02:59.979
Were you seeing anyone get shot?

00:02:59.979 --> 00:03:00.480
Yeah.

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:02.682
You can see people fall.

00:03:02.682 --> 00:03:04.050
It's 8:30 a.m.

00:03:04.050 --> 00:03:05.151
and as Gale and others

00:03:05.151 --> 00:03:06.786
continued running east,

00:03:06.786 --> 00:03:08.188
others running north met

00:03:08.188 --> 00:03:10.790
with more bullets and a police blockade,

00:03:10.790 --> 00:03:13.393
causing further panic.

00:03:13.393 --> 00:03:14.627
As a result, revelers

00:03:14.627 --> 00:03:15.995
start running back down

00:03:15.995 --> 00:03:18.231
the main road towards the festival,

00:03:18.231 --> 00:03:19.966
not knowing there were more militants.

00:03:19.966 --> 00:03:23.069
Just a few kilometers further down

00:03:23.136 --> 00:03:24.237
on that same road.

00:03:24.237 --> 00:03:26.139
Chilling dash cam footage shows

00:03:26.139 --> 00:03:28.241
Hamas militants shooting directly

00:03:28.241 --> 00:03:29.776
at an approaching car

00:03:29.776 --> 00:03:32.178
just an hour earlier.

00:03:32.178 --> 00:03:33.313
Those festival goers

00:03:33.313 --> 00:03:35.615
that remained closer to the concert site

00:03:35.615 --> 00:03:38.017
hid behind anything they could find,

00:03:38.017 --> 00:03:39.419
even behind trees

00:03:39.419 --> 00:03:41.120
waiting while the bullets closed.

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:42.722
And

00:03:42.722 --> 00:03:44.757
many did not survive.

00:03:44.757 --> 00:03:47.260
260 are reported dead,

00:03:47.260 --> 00:03:50.129
but that toll could rise.

00:03:50.129 --> 00:03:51.331
Just 3 hours

00:03:51.331 --> 00:03:52.899
after the start of the massacre,

00:03:52.899 --> 00:03:54.734
a 9:39 a.m.

00:03:54.734 --> 00:03:55.602
videos emerge

00:03:55.602 --> 00:03:56.769
of some festival goers

00:03:56.769 --> 00:03:59.405
already held hostage in Gaza.

00:03:59.405 --> 00:04:00.707
This man still wearing

00:04:00.707 --> 00:04:02.208
a festival wristband

00:04:02.208 --> 00:04:03.276
and another visibly

00:04:03.276 --> 00:04:05.578
wearing the security uniform.

00:04:05.578 --> 00:04:08.114
Their fates remain unknown.

00:04:08.114 --> 00:04:09.983
Google and others are still processing

00:04:09.983 --> 00:04:11.784
the trauma of what they went through.

00:04:11.784 --> 00:04:12.986
I know people who were like

00:04:12.986 --> 00:04:14.287
12 hours in the bushes

00:04:14.287 --> 00:04:15.955
and they didn't move.

00:04:15.955 --> 00:04:17.957
I know people who tried to hide

00:04:17.957 --> 00:04:19.292
and they died.

00:04:19.292 --> 00:04:21.995
Humanity never seen this

00:04:21.995 --> 00:04:24.530
in the last couple of hundreds of years

00:04:24.530 --> 00:04:27.900
since maybe the Holocaust.

00:04:27.967 --> 00:04:30.336
But this is just this is just horrific.

00:04:30.336 --> 00:04:32.138
Horrific.

00:04:32.138 --> 00:04:34.741
It would be 10 hours until help arrived

00:04:34.741 --> 00:04:35.675
for some.

00:04:35.675 --> 00:04:37.176
Others are still missing,

00:04:37.176 --> 00:04:40.146
feared dead or held hostage in Gaza.

00:04:40.146 --> 00:04:41.914
The scale of this tragedy

00:04:41.914 --> 00:04:43.449
may grow greater yet

00:04:43.449 --> 00:04:45.285
after those 6 hours of horror

00:04:45.285 --> 00:04:46.219
in the desert.

00:04:46.219 --> 00:04:51.391
Katie Polglase, CNN, London.

00:04:51.457 --> 00:04:53.326
And OUTFRONT now, Wolf BLITZER.

00:04:53.326 --> 00:04:53.826
Of course,

00:04:53.826 --> 00:04:54.994
he's been following this

00:04:54.994 --> 00:04:56.262
story for decades

00:04:56.262 --> 00:04:57.964
and he knows it better than anyone.

00:04:57.964 --> 00:05:00.300
So, Wolf, when you look at that report

00:05:00.300 --> 00:05:02.335
