00:05:04.837 --> 00:05:05.672
the slaughter of at least

00:05:05.672 --> 00:05:06.906
260 people,

00:05:06.906 --> 00:05:09.075
that the footage of someone

00:05:09.075 --> 00:05:09.909
shooting up the port

00:05:09.909 --> 00:05:12.011
a potties for shelter to shelter

00:05:12.011 --> 00:05:13.179
because they knew where they were

00:05:13.179 --> 00:05:14.113
waiting to be brought in them

00:05:14.113 --> 00:05:15.982
