00:05:15.982 --> 00:05:17.517
The more we find out, the harder

00:05:17.517 --> 00:05:18.618
it is to see a way for this

00:05:18.618 --> 00:05:19.285
to to

00:05:19.285 --> 00:05:19.986
to de-escalate,

00:05:19.986 --> 00:05:22.388
for anyone to to back away.

00:05:22.388 --> 00:05:24.157
And I know yesterday you and I spoke,

00:05:24.157 --> 00:05:26.259
you thought there was a very tiny chance

00:05:26.259 --> 00:05:26.926
that this

00:05:26.926 --> 00:05:27.393
this could

00:05:27.393 --> 00:05:28.161
this could calm down

00:05:28.161 --> 00:05:29.395
and de-escalate

00:05:29.395 --> 00:05:30.396
as that chance

00:05:30.396 --> 00:05:32.298
basically gone to zero now?

00:05:32.298 --> 00:05:34.300
Yes, it's basically zero

00:05:34.300 --> 00:05:35.234
based on everything I'm

00:05:35.234 --> 00:05:37.937
hearing from my Israeli sources.

00:05:37.937 --> 00:05:39.706
The Israeli military does not

00:05:39.706 --> 00:05:41.574
mobilize 300,000

00:05:41.574 --> 00:05:43.876
or maybe close to 400,000 troops,

00:05:43.876 --> 00:05:46.746
deploys them to this area around Gaza

00:05:46.746 --> 00:05:48.881
and is not about to try to achieve

00:05:48.881 --> 00:05:50.450
two major objectives.

00:05:50.450 --> 00:05:51.784
The first objective

00:05:51.784 --> 00:05:52.919
to either capture

00:05:52.919 --> 00:05:55.221
or kill the Hamas leadership.

00:05:55.221 --> 00:05:55.688
The second

00:05:55.688 --> 00:05:56.823
objective to either

00:05:56.823 --> 00:05:59.826
capture or destroy the Hamas weapons.

00:05:59.826 --> 00:06:00.760
They'd like to capture

00:06:00.760 --> 00:06:01.627
a lot of those weapons

00:06:01.627 --> 00:06:03.663
