00:06:10.269 --> 00:06:12.472
that that creates a moment

00:06:12.472 --> 00:06:13.339
for the Israelis

00:06:13.339 --> 00:06:15.708
if they want to continue the escalation

00:06:15.708 --> 00:06:18.044
to target some sort of objectives

00:06:18.044 --> 00:06:19.145
in Iran as well.

00:06:19.145 --> 00:06:20.613
This could really escalate

00:06:20.613 --> 00:06:23.349
not just in Gaza, but elsewhere as well.

00:06:23.349 --> 00:06:26.018
And I'm convinced that the Israelis

00:06:26.018 --> 00:06:27.186
are not going to back away.

00:06:27.186 --> 00:06:29.522
They want achieve those two objectives.

00:06:29.522 --> 00:06:31.324
It could happen within a matter of hours.

00:06:31.324 --> 00:06:31.958
It could happen

00:06:31.958 --> 00:06:33.726
within a matter of a few days.

00:06:33.726 --> 00:06:35.094
But everyone should brace

00:06:35.094 --> 00:06:36.462
for a major Israeli

00:06:36.462 --> 00:06:40.366
ground invasion of Gaza.

